    MCP_CLIENT --> MCP_SECRETS
    MCP_CLIENT --> MCP_IaC

    MCP_K8S --> AUTHZ
    MCP_OBSERV --> AUTHZ
    MCP_SECRETS --> AUTHZ
    MCP_IaC --> APPROVAL
    AUTHZ --> AUDIT
    APPROVAL --> AUDIT

